nodes.text: World of Reading Star Wars Boxed Set: Level 2

World of Reading Star Wars Boxed Set: Level 2 is a collection of six Star Wars young-reader books in the World of Reading Level 2 series. The included titles are Trouble on Tatooine, Trapped in the Death Star!, Use the Force!, Captured on Cloud City, Rescue from Jabba's Palace, and The Fight in the Forest. The set was published by Disney–Lucasfilm Press on July 11, 2017.
